      "title": "Man arrested for hoarding 600 liters of diesel in Manipur",
      "author": "T Yuwaraj",
      "body_lines": [
        "In Jaffna, Special Task Force (STF) arrested a man on charges of hoarding 600 liters of diesel.",
        "The arrest took place tonight at a house near the school in Manipay.",
        "It is noteworthy that the suspect has been referred to the Manipay police station for further court proceedings."
      ],
